## 🚀 Quick Start

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/{{config.repositoryName}}.git
   cd {{config.repositoryName}}
   ```

2. **Set up the database**
   ```bash
   docker-compose up -d
   ```

3. **Install dependencies**
{{#config.language}}
{{#equals language "python"}}
